On top of the standard up-to-the-minute reporting on the current state of your business, you can analyze day-to-day and week-to-week changes in opportunities, cases, forecasts, and custom objects.

Track Changes Over Time with Historical Trend Reporting
Historical trend reporting uses a special custom report type designed to highlight changes between five snapshot dates. You can visually represent the data changes in charts and on dashboards.

Report on Historical Data with Reporting Snapshots
A reporting snapshot lets you report on historical data. Authorized users can save tabular or summary report results to fields on a custom object, then map those fields to corresponding fields on a target object.
